{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place peppercorns in mixing bowl and crush <b>10 sec\/speed 7<b>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place butter and shallots in mixing bowl and chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>. Sauté <b>5 min\/120°C\/speed 0.5<b>.","Add brandy and, without measuring cup, cook <b>3 min\/100°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add stock, reserved crushed peppercorns and ground black pepper then, without measuring cup, heat <b>8 min\/100°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add dissolved cornflour and heat <b>2 min\/100°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add cream and heat <b>2 min\/100°C\/speed 2<b>. Adjust seasoning to taste then pour into a warmed jug before serving."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["1 Tbsp pink peppercorns","1 Tbsp white peppercorns","1 Tbsp black peppercorns","60 g butter, diced","45 g shallots, halved","100 g brandy","130 g beef stock","1 pinch ground black pepper,  or to taste","1 Tbsp cornflour, dissolved in 1 Tbsp water","60 g double cream","fine sea salt, to taste"]}],"id":"r108250","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-HQaD2y3cxk8\/XZaeJDLa17I\/AAAAAAAAgjI\/aMcC2mG9Ja4pe6KiPpmTbixw27XDg-79gCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_Q2nViLC-mW4iqFyt.png","title":"Peppercorn Sauce","publishedAt":"2016-09-05T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"1.1 g","fat":"20 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"8.1 g","calories":"905 kJ \/ 216 kcal"},"basicInfo":["easy","10m","30m","4 portions"]}